Package: pusher
Title: Push Future-Dated Git Commits When Due
Version: 0.0.4
Authors@R: person("Mark", "Heckmann", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "mark@example.com")
Author: Mark Heckmann [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Mark Heckmann <mark@example.com>
Description: Tracks local Git repositories and pushes unpublished commits when
    the later of their author and committer dates has been reached.
